import React from 'react' export const SSCMTSTeirI = () => { return (
Name of Post:

SSC MTS & Havaldar Recruitment 2021 Paper I Exam Application Status / Admit Card 2022
Post Date / Update: 27 June 2022 | 10:41 AM
Short Information : Staff Selection Commission SSC Admit Card & Status of SSC Multi Tasking Staff MTS & Havaldar Recruitment 2021 Written CBT Exam starting from 05th July 2022. All the candidates who are registered in this recruitment of SSC can see their admit card and status.

Staff Selection Commission (SSC)

SSC Multi Tasking Staff MTS Status / Admit Card Download 2022

SSC MTS Paper I Exam 2021 - Short Details of Notification

WWW.SARKARIRESULT.COM

Important Dates

  • Tier II CBT Exam Date : 05-26 July 2022
  • Status / Admit Card Available : 25/06/2022

MTS Exam Conducted By

  • Staff Selection Commission SSC Central Region CR, NR, MPR, KKR & Other Region Are Conducted the Multi Tasking Staff MTS & Havaldar Recruitment 2021 Paper CBT Exam Held on 05-22 July 2022.

Eligibility to Download SSC MTS & Havaldar Paper I Admit Card 2022

  • Candidates Who Are Enrolled with Staff Selection Commission SSC Multi Tasking Staff & Havaldar Recruitment 2021 Are Eligible to Download Tier I Exam Admit Card and Check the Application Status.

How to Download MTS 2021 Paper I Exams Admit Card / Status 2022
